<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Activate Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      header h1 {
        color: white;
      }
      main {
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .activation-code {
        font-size: 2em;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #4caf50;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Learning Management System</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <h1>Activate Your Account</h1>
      <p>
        Hello <b> <%= user.name %> </b> We're excited to have you on board! To
        get started, please enter the four-digit code we sent to your email
        address.
      </p>
      <p class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></p>
      <p>
        Once you've entered the code, you'll be able to set up your profile and
        start exploring our courses.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
